Proportion and Total Diverted

diversions.Rd

Monthly propotion and total diverted values for the duration of screw trap observations.

amer_tot_div

moke_tot_div

stan_tot_div

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 240 rows and 3 columns.

Details

Available screw trap data start and end years:

Locationstart-end
Feather River1998 - 2016
American River2013 - 2016
Clear Creek1998 - 2016
Mokelumne River1999 - 2015
Stanislaus River1998 - 2016

Proportion Diverted

Values pre September 2003 are CALSIM model output and values after are the median CALSIM value grouped by water year type and month.

For more details on CALSIM see:

  • use this link within R proportion_diverted

  • use this link if in a web browser

NOTE: No major diversions to track for Clear Creek.

Mokelumne data is measured provided by EDMUD

Total Diverted

Values were estimated by multiplying the measured flow data and the modeled proportion diverted values.

NOTE: Mokelumne data is measured provided by EDMUD
